data.name: labelKeyboardInstructions.Values.Text
data.value:
Use the ALT or F10 key to enter KeyTips mode.
Now use the either the LEFT, RIGHT or TAB keys to move from KeyTips to simple keyboard navigation. You can use the SPACE or DOWN keys when on an appropriate item to action it.

data.name: labelKeyTipInstructions.Values.Text
data.value:
Use the ALT or F10 key to enter KeyTips mode.
Quick access toolbar buttons are auto allocated numbers for their KeyTips with 00 always used for the overflow button when it is present.
You can access collapsed groups by using the present KeyTip and it will show a popup for the group along with KeyTips. Use the ESCAPE key to move back a level.
